  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A New Blend of Arena-Survival</h2>Mechabot Defender is an arcade arena-survival game with light tower defence elements, unique characters, classes, bosses, and a wide variety of upgrades. There are many mechanics and challenges at play in Mechabot Defender, so picking the right upgrades and using your unique character ability efficiently will be crucial to your success.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950820/extras/c2248b9bb2e2f56d37c288c1dc145561.poster.avif?t=1695669161\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950820/extras/c2248b9bb2e2f56d37c288c1dc145561.webm?t=1695669161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950820/extras/c2248b9bb2e2f56d37c288c1dc145561.mp4?t=1695669161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Twists</h2>You must rely on your turrets to protect you from the horde -- collect energy from enemies that can be used to activate the ultimate abilities of eight different turret classes, as well as your character's own unique ability.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950820/extras/7b41580f0a767afe809f17d42e65b55a.poster.avif?t=1695669161\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950820/extras/7b41580f0a767afe809f17d42e65b55a.webm?t=1695669161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950820/extras/7b41580f0a767afe809f17d42e65b55a.mp4?t=1695669161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Builds Every Run</h2>Each turret can be upgraded individually with a broad variety of different upgrades!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950820/extras/267d54d5b5b94e40e4898fa68d47fd5d.poster.avif?t=1695669161\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950820/extras/267d54d5b5b94e40e4898fa68d47fd5d.webm?t=1695669161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950820/extras/267d54d5b5b94e40e4898fa68d47fd5d.mp4?t=1695669161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br>🔲  Upgrade your turrets separately and create two completely unique synergies!<br>🔲  Challenging gameplay that doesn't hold your hand.<br>🔲  Characters and Classes to be unlocked.<br>🔲  A mixture of automatic and manual control: let your turrets handle it, or tether to them to aim yourself!<br>🔲  Several unique enemies with their own behaviours and gimmicks.<br>🔲  3 Unique Stages with their own Unique Bosses!",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A New Blend of Arena-Survival</h2>Mechabot Defender is an arcade arena-survival game with light tower defence elements, unique characters, classes, bosses, and a wide variety of upgrades. There are many mechanics and challenges at play in Mechabot Defender, so picking the right upgrades and using your unique character ability efficiently will be crucial to your success.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950820/extras/c2248b9bb2e2f56d37c288c1dc145561.poster.avif?t=1695669161\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950820/extras/c2248b9bb2e2f56d37c288c1dc145561.webm?t=1695669161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950820/extras/c2248b9bb2e2f56d37c288c1dc145561.mp4?t=1695669161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Twists</h2>You must rely on your turrets to protect you from the horde -- collect energy from enemies that can be used to activate the ultimate abilities of eight different turret classes, as well as your character's own unique ability.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950820/extras/7b41580f0a767afe809f17d42e65b55a.poster.avif?t=1695669161\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950820/extras/7b41580f0a767afe809f17d42e65b55a.webm?t=1695669161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950820/extras/7b41580f0a767afe809f17d42e65b55a.mp4?t=1695669161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Builds Every Run</h2>Each turret can be upgraded individually with a broad variety of different upgrades!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950820/extras/267d54d5b5b94e40e4898fa68d47fd5d.poster.avif?t=1695669161\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950820/extras/267d54d5b5b94e40e4898fa68d47fd5d.webm?t=1695669161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1950820/extras/267d54d5b5b94e40e4898fa68d47fd5d.mp4?t=1695669161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br>🔲  Upgrade your turrets separately and create two completely unique synergies!<br>🔲  Challenging gameplay that doesn't hold your hand.<br>🔲  Characters and Classes to be unlocked.<br>🔲  A mixture of automatic and manual control: let your turrets handle it, or tether to them to aim yourself!<br>🔲  Several unique enemies with their own behaviours and gimmicks.<br>🔲  3 Unique Stages with their own Unique Bosses!",
